MOTION DOCKET

95-64. State ex rel. Crandall, Phiels & Wisniewski v. DeCessna.

In Procedendo and Prohibition. On motion for order to show cause and on motion to strike relators’ motion to show cause. Sua sponte, alternative writ granted.

Cook, J., dissents. Resnick, J., not participating.
